---
import CheckmarkIcon from "@/assets/icons/checkmark.svg";
import QuoteIcon from "@/assets/icons/quote.svg";
---

<style>
  .radar-chart {
    --chart-grid-stroke: oklch(83.2% 0.035 255 / 0.4);
    --chart-data-stroke: oklch(36.9% 0.051 316);
    --chart-data-fill: oklch(36.9% 0.051 316 / 0.15);
    --chart-label-fill: oklch(36.9% 0.051 316 / 0.7);
  }
</style>

<section
  class="value-proposal-section bg-soft-bg relative overflow-hidden py-16 lg:py-24"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mx-auto mb-12 max-w-4xl text-center lg:mb-16">
      <h2
        class="value-proposal-title text-purple-dark mb-6 text-3xl leading-tight font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
      >
        Un acompañamiento terapéutico que se ajusta a tus necesidades.
      </h2>

      <p
        class="value-proposal-subtitle text-purple-dark/75 mx-auto max-w-3xl text-base leading-relaxed italic md:text-lg"
      >
        Aquí exploraremos cómo funciona mi método. La psicología tradicional a
        veces puede sentirse fría o rígida. Mi enfoque es <strong
          class="text-purple-dark font-semibold not-italic"
          >Pluralista y Humano</strong
        >. El siguiente gráfico ilustra cómo integramos diferentes escuelas
        psicológicas para crear un proceso personalizado y equilibrado para ti.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Two-column layout -->
    <div
      class="value-proposal-content mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-6"
    >
      <!-- Left Column: Text Content -->
      <div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-8">
        <!-- Approach explanation -->
        <div class="approach-text">
          <p class="text-purple-dark/80 text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg">
            Integro herramientas de la <strong
              class="text-purple-dark font-semibold"
              >Terapia Cognitivo-Conductual</strong
            > (para el cambio práctico), el <strong
              class="text-purple-dark font-semibold">Humanismo</strong
            > (para validar tu emoción) y la <strong
              class="text-purple-dark font-semibold"
              >Mirada Sistémica / Psicodinámica</strong
            > para explorar los procesos profundos que influyen en tu historia y en
            tu forma de relacionarte.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quote box -->
        <div
          class="quote-box bg-soft-beige relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm lg:p-8"
        >
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <QuoteIcon
              class="text-purple-accent/30 mb-3 h-8 w-8 lg:h-10 lg:w-10"
            />
            <p
              class="text-purple-dark/85 text-base leading-relaxed italic lg:text-lg"
            >
              ¿El resultado? Es un espacio seguro y personalizado, donde no solo
              te escucho, sino que te acompaño con herramientas concretas para
              favorecer un proceso de comprensión y cambio genuino.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Decorative background element -->
          <div
            class="bg-purple-accent/5 pointer-events-none absolute -right-6 -bottom-6 h-24 w-24 rounded-full blur-2xl"
          >
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Checkmark list -->
        <div class="checkmark-list space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div
              class="bg-olive/20 flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
            >
              <CheckmarkIcon class="text-olive h-4 w-4" />
            </div>
            <p class="text-purple-dark/80 text-base leading-relaxed lg:text-lg">
              Espacio 100% libre de juicios.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div
              class="bg-olive/20 flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
            >
              <CheckmarkIcon class="text-olive h-4 w-4" />
            </div>
            <p class="text-purple-dark/80 text-base leading-relaxed lg:text-lg">
              Enfoque práctico orientado a soluciones.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div
              class="bg-olive/20 flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
            >
              <CheckmarkIcon class="text-olive h-4 w-4" />
            </div>
            <p class="text-purple-dark/80 text-base leading-relaxed lg:text-lg">
              Experiencia especializada con población migrante.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Radar Chart -->
      <div
        class="radar-chart-container bg-soft-beige mx-auto w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-2xl"
      >
        <!-- Title -->
        <div class="mb-6 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-purple-dark text-xl font-bold">
            Equilibrio del Enfoque Pluralista
          </h2>
          <p class="text-purple-dark/60 mt-1 text-sm">
            Integración de dimensiones terapéuticas
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Chart container -->
        <div class="chart-wrapper relative flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 400 380"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="radar-chart w-full max-w-sm"
            aria-label="Gráfico radar del Enfoque Pluralista"
          >
            <!-- ── GRID PENTAGONS (5 levels, lightest = outermost) ── -->
            <g stroke="var(--chart-grid-stroke)" stroke-width="1" fill="none">
              <!-- Level 5 (outermost) -->
              <polygon points="200,65 323,152 276,298 124,298 77,152"></polygon>
              <!-- Level 4 -->
              <polygon points="200,91 307,165 265,280 135,280 93,165"></polygon>
              <!-- Level 3 -->
              <polygon points="200,117 291,178 254,262 146,262 109,178"
              ></polygon>
              <!-- Level 2 -->
              <polygon points="200,143 275,191 243,244 157,244 125,191"
              ></polygon>
              <!-- Level 1 (innermost) -->
              <polygon points="200,169 259,204 232,226 168,226 141,204"
              ></polygon>
            </g>

            <!-- ── AXIS LINES (center to each vertex of outermost pentagon) ── -->
            <g stroke="var(--chart-grid-stroke)" stroke-width="1">
              <line x1="200" y1="195" x2="200" y2="65"></line>
              <!-- top -->
              <line x1="200" y1="195" x2="323" y2="152"></line>
              <!-- top-right -->
              <line x1="200" y1="195" x2="276" y2="298"></line>
              <!-- bottom-right -->
              <line x1="200" y1="195" x2="124" y2="298"></line>
              <!-- bottom-left -->
              <line x1="200" y1="195" x2="77" y2="152"></line>
              <!-- top-left -->
            </g>

            <polygon
              points="200,117 304.6,161 222.9,226.6 184.7,216 144.9,177.1"
              fill="var(--chart-data-fill)"
              stroke="var(--chart-data-stroke)"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linejoin="round"></polygon>

            <!-- ── DATA POINTS (dots on vertices) ── -->
            <g fill="var(--chart-data-stroke)">
              <circle cx="200" cy="117" r="5"></circle>
              <circle cx="304.6" cy="161" r="5"></circle>
              <circle cx="222.9" cy="226.6" r="5"></circle>
              <circle cx="184.7" cy="216" r="5"></circle>
              <circle cx="144.9" cy="177.1" r="5"></circle>
            </g>

            <!-- ── LABELS ── -->
            <g
              font-size="11"
              fill="var(--chart-label-fill)"
              font-family="sans-serif"
              text-anchor="middle"
            >
              <!-- Acción Práctica (TCC) — top -->
              <text x="200" y="53" class="text-purple-dark font-bold"
                >Acción Práctica (TCC)</text
              >

              <!-- Validación Emocional — top-right -->
              <text x="345" y="150" class="text-purple-dark font-bold"
                >Validación Emocional</text
              >

              <!-- Raíces Profundas — bottom-right -->
              <text x="310" y="318" class="text-purple-dark font-bold"
                >Raíces Profundas</text
              >

              <!-- Contexto Sistémico — bottom-left -->
              <text x="98" y="318" class="text-purple-dark font-bold"
                >Contexto Sistémico</text
              >

              <!-- Resolución de Duelos — top-left -->
              <text x="60" y="150" class="text-purple-dark font-bold"
                >Resolución de Duelos</text
              >
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import { valueProposalAnimations } from "@/utils/animations/home/valueProposal.Animations.js";

  // Initialize animations
  valueProposalAnimations();
</script>
